<i>noun</i>: 좌충우돌 [좌ː충우돌] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>좌충우돌 [좌ː충우돌]</dt><br>
<dd>stumbling</dd><br>
<dd>이쪽 저쪽으로 돌아가며 사람이나 사물을 분별없이 치고받고 부딪히는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of moving in different directions to bump into and collide with people or objects at random.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>